      - text: 哦？
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "你要在我們的驛站住宿嗎？\n趁這機會你就聽我說說吧。\n從這裡往南走一段路，\n會走到一座叫"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 瓦舒阿山丘
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "的山丘。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: 那裡有個不知來歷的謎樣台座……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n完全沒人知道那到底是什麼。\n唉……果戈大哥跟我要到何時\n才能解開謎團呢……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
  talk01:
    attributes: Npc_HyruleWestHatago006
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: "想看謎樣台座，\n就去位於南方的"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 瓦舒阿山丘
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: 瞧瞧吧。
  talk02:
    attributes: Npc_HyruleWestHatago006
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 10
            - 0
      - text: 咦？什麼？跑出
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 古代神廟
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "來！？\n那個台座竟然藏著如此謎團啊！"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: 好！這次一定要解開那座神廟的謎團！
  talk03:
    attributes: Npc_HyruleWestHatago006
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: 這次換
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 古代神廟
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: ……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n謎團真是越來越深了……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
  talk04:
    attributes: Npc_HyruleWestHatago006
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: "唉～現在根本不是照顧\n白山羊的時候啊……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
  talk05:
    attributes: Npc_HyruleWestHatago006
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 11
            - 0
      - text: "唉～現在根本不是\n在這裡喝的時候啊……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
  talk06:
    attributes: Npc_HyruleWestHatago006
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 0
      - text: 這麼說來，有個
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
      - text: 利特族
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "的老兄\n聽說這件事之後，就往南方飛去了。\n是帶著大樂器的吟遊詩人。\n他一定是去看台座的。"
